{"tid":1520420,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"光復香港 時代革命 • 五大訴求 缺一不可","createTime":"2019-08-30T19:27:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T19:42:17.000Z","uid":4215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b3b4ef78a9eb58ea0cc3405e49d63719a64d5626","tid":1520420,"uid":4215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T19:27:26.000Z","msg":"無論聽日戰線喺邊 都要記住<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不受傷 不被捕</span></span><br />\n支共今日做左咁多野都係想我地自亂陣腳<br />\n但我地更加要冷靜唔好一味比憤怒掩蓋我地雙眼<br />\n只要同佢鬥長命 我地就會贏<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢場係一場持久戰</span></span><br />\n<br />\n從來無見大家嘅樣貌 但呢兩個月我地都感受到<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最美的風景是人</span></span><br />\n好想喺煲底除哂gear同大家相聚<br />\n好好地傾計 唔洗戴住豬嘴唔撚知大家講乜鳩<br />\n大家就係彼此最強嘅後盾<br />\n應承我 應承大家<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不受傷 不被捕</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"51386042686284b1dd43d0cd0bccddab79227409","tid":1520420,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T19:27:48.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會 港島見<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=